<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>FC01-0001287 · Nota De Crédito Electrónica</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { margin: 0; }
  :root {
    --ink: #0f0f10;
    --ink-2: #4a4a50;
    --ink-3: #8c8c94;
    --accent: #ff5a1f;
    --accent-soft: #fff1ea;
    --line: #e8e6df;
    --paper: #fbfaf4;
  }
  body {
    font-family: 'Archivo', sans-serif;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper);
    width: 302px;
    min-height: auto;
    padding: 16px;
    min-height: 1123px;
    padding: 36px 40px;
  }
  .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  p { margin: 0; }

  .hero { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 290px; gap: 24px; align-items: stretch; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .hero .left { padding: 22px 24px; border: 1.5px solid var(--ink); border-radius: 4px; background: #fff; }
  .hero .left .mark { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .hero .left .logo { width: 44px; height: 44px; background: var(--ink); color: var(--accent); border-radius: 2px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .hero .left .logo svg { width: 26px; height: 26px; }
  .hero .left .co-name { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 1.1; }
  .hero .left .co-tag { font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-2); margin-top: 2px; font-weight: 500; }
  .hero .left .info { font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-2); }
  .hero .left .info p { padding: 1px 0; }
  .hero .left .info b { color: var(--ink); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }

  .hero .right { padding: 20px 22px; background: var(--ink); color: #fff; border-radius: 4px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }
  .hero .right .kind { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .hero .right .num { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 4px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .hero .right .rule { height: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18); margin: 12px 0; }
  .hero .right .row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 10px; padding: 1.5px 0; }
  .hero .right .row .k { opacity: 0.62; }
  .hero .right .row .v { font-weight: 500; }

  .parties { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .party { background: #fff; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 14px 16px; position: relative; }
  .party::before { content: ""; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 14px; bottom: 14px; width: 3px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 0 2px 2px 0; }
  .party .label { font-size: 9px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.16em; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .party .name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 5px; letter-spacing: -0.005em; }
  .party .row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 72px 1fr; font-size: 10px; padding: 1px 0; }
  .party .row .k { color: var(--ink-3); }

  .items-wrap { background: #fff; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--line); overflow: hidden; }
  .items { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
  .items thead th { font-size: 9.5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #fff; font-weight: 700; text-align: left; padding: 12px 12px; background: var(--ink); }
  .items tbody td { padding: 10px 12px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); vertical-align: top; font-size: 9.5px; }
  .items .c-idx { width: 34px; text-align: center; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
  .items .c-code { width: 90px; }
  .items .c-qty, .items .c-price, .items .c-tax { text-align: right; }
  .items .c-qty { width: 60px; }
  .items .c-unit { width: 50px; text-align: center; color: var(--ink-3); }
  .items .c-price { width: 82px; }
  .items .c-tax { width: 90px; font-weight: 600; }
  .items .desc .main { font-weight: 600; }
  .items .desc .sub { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--ink-3); margin-top: 2px; font-weight: 400; }

  .bottom { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px; gap: 14px; margin-top: 14px; }
  .notes .block { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 4px; padding: 10px 12px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .notes .block .head { font-size: 9px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .notes .block .body { font-size: 10px; }
  .notes .block .body p + p { margin-top: 2px; }
  .notes .small { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--ink-2); }

  .totals { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
  .totals .inner { padding: 12px 16px; }
  .totals .line { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 3px 0; font-size: 9.5px; }
  .totals .line .k { color: var(--ink-2); }
  .totals .line .v { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; white-space: nowrap; }
  .totals .rule { border-top: 1px dashed var(--line); margin: 6px 0; }
  .totals .grand-wrap { background: var(--accent); color: var(--ink); padding: 14px 16px; }
  .totals .grand { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; }
  .totals .grand .k { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.16em; font-weight: 800; }
  .totals .grand .v { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.01em; white-space: nowrap; }
  .totals .grand-wrap .words { font-size: 9.5px; margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 500; }

  .foot { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 96px 1fr auto; gap: 18px; align-items: start; margin-top: 18px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 2px solid var(--ink); }
  .foot .qr { width: 96px; height: 96px; background: #fff; padding: 4px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1.5px solid var(--ink); }
  .foot .qr svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; display: block; }
  .foot .meta { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--ink-2); }
  .foot .meta strong { color: var(--ink); }
  .foot .meta .hash { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; word-break: break-all; font-size: 8.5px; margin-top: 4px; color: var(--ink-3); }
  .foot .stamp { text-align: right; min-width: 180px; }
  .foot .stamp .badge { display: inline-block; background: var(--ink); color: var(--accent); padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .foot .stamp .line { font-size: 9.5px; color: var(--ink-2); margin-top: 8px; max-width: 190px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="left">
    <div class="mark">
      <div class="logo">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
          <rect x="6" y="6" width="28" height="28" rx="2"/>
          <path d="M12 20h16M12 14h10M12 26h14"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="co-name">MANUFACTURAS ANDINA TEXTIL</div>
        <div class="co-tag">Premium textiles since 2001 — Lima, Perú</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info">
      <p>{{ doc.company.address.direccion }} — Cercado de Lima</p>
      <p>ventas@andinatextil.pe · (01) 555-0102 · andinatextil.pe</p>
      <p>RUC <b>{{ doc.company.ruc }}</b></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="right">
    <div>
      <div class="kind">Nota De Crédito Electrónica</div>
      <div class="num">FC01-0001287</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="rule"></div>
      <div class="row"><span class="k">Emitido</span><span class="v">{{ doc.fechaEmision|date('d/m/Y') }} · 14:32</span></div>
      <div class="row"><span class="k">Vence</span><span class="v">24/05/2026</span></div>
      <div class="row"><span class="k">Moneda</span><span class="v">Soles · T/C 3.742</span></div>
      <div class="row"><span class="k">Condición</span><span class="v">Crédito · 2 cuotas</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="parties">
  <div class="party">
    <div class="label">Cliente</div>
    <div class="name">{{ cl.rznSocial }}</div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">RUC</span><span class="mono">{{ cl.numDoc }}</span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">Dirección</span><span>{{ cl.address.direccion }}</span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">Ubicación</span><span>Lima — Lima — Miraflores</span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">O/C</span><span class="mono">OC-2026-00487</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="party">
    <div class="label">Operación</div>
    <div class="name">0101 — VENTA INTERNA</div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">Entrega</span><span>Almacén Los Portales · Callao</span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">Guía</span><span class="mono">GRE T001-00452</span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">Vendedor</span><span>Diego Paredes</span></div>
    <div class="row"><span class="k">Ruta</span><span>Lima–Callao</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="items-wrap">
<table class="items">
  <thead>
    <tr><th class="c-idx">#</th><th class="c-code">Código</th><th>Descripción</th><th class="c-unit">Und</th><th class="c-qty">Cant.</th><th class="c-price">P. Unit.</th><th class="c-tax">Importe</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>

    {% for det in doc.details %}
    <tr>
      <td class="c-idx mono">{{ loop.index|str_pad(2, '0', 'left') }}</td>
      <td class="c-code mono">{{ det.codProducto }}</td>
      <td class="desc"><div class="main">{{ det.descripcion }}</div><div class="sub">{% if det.codProductoSUNAT %}SUNAT {{ det.codProductoSUNAT }}{% endif %}</div></td>
      <td class="c-unit">{{ det.unidad }}</td>
      <td class="c-qty mono">{{ det.cantidad|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="c-price mono">{{ det.mtoValorUnitario|n_format }}</td>
      <td class="c-tax mono">{{ det.mtoValorVenta|n_format }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>
</div>

<div class="bottom">
  <div class="notes">
    <div class="block"><div class="head">Cuotas</div><div class="body">
      <p class="small">Cuota 1 · 24/05/2026 · <b>{{ moneda }} 5,946.20</b></p>
      <p class="small">Cuota 2 · 24/06/2026 · <b>{{ moneda }} 5,946.20</b></p>
    </div></div>
    <div class="block"><div class="head">Detracción</div><div class="body">
      <p><b>{{ moneda }} 1,427.09</b> · 020 Bienes gravados con IGV</p>
      <p class="small">Transferencia en cuenta · Cta. BN 00-032-019287</p>
    </div></div>
    <div class="block"><div class="head">Observaciones</div><div class="body">
      <p>Pedido fraccionado — entrega en 2 camiones.</p>
    </div></div>
    <div class="block"><div class="head">Leyendas SUNAT</div><div class="body">
      <p class="small">· SON ONCE MIL OCHOCIENTOS NOVENTA Y DOS CON 40/100 {{ moneda }}</p>
      <p class="small">· Operación sujeta a detracción</p>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="totals">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="line"><span class="k">Op. gravadas</span><span class="v">{{ moneda }} {{ doc.mtoOperGravadas|n_format }}</span></div>
      <div class="line"><span class="k">Op. exoneradas</span><span class="v">{{ moneda }} 0.00</span></div>
      <div class="line"><span class="k">Op. inafectas</span><span class="v">{{ moneda }} 0.00</span></div>
      <div class="line"><span class="k">Op. gratuitas</span><span class="v">{{ moneda }} 0.00</span></div>
      <div class="rule"></div>
      <div class="line"><span class="k">IGV (18%)</span><span class="v">{{ moneda }} {{ doc.mtoIGV|n_format }}</span></div>
      <div class="line"><span class="k">ICBPER / ISC</span><span class="v">{{ moneda }} 0.00</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grand-wrap">
      <div class="grand"><span class="k">Total</span><span class="v">{{ moneda }} {{ doc.mtoImpVenta|n_format }}</span></div>
      <div class="words">Son: once mil ochocientos noventa y dos con 40/100 soles.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="foot">
  <div class="qr">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 21 21" shape-rendering="crispEdges"><rect width="21" height="21" fill="#fff"/>
    <g fill="#0f0f10">
      <rect x="0" y="0" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="1" y="1" width="5" height="5" fill="#fff"/><rect x="2" y="2" width="3" height="3"/>
      <rect x="14" y="0" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="15" y="1" width="5" height="5" fill="#fff"/><rect x="16" y="2" width="3" height="3"/>
      <rect x="0" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="1" y="15" width="5" height="5" fill="#fff"/><rect x="2" y="16" width="3" height="3"/>
      <rect x="8" y="0" width="1" height="1"/><rect x="10" y="0" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="8" y="2" width="2" height="1"/>
      <rect x="5" y="8" width="2" height="2"/><rect x="8" y="8" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="11" y="8" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="13" y="8" width="3" height="1"/><rect x="17" y="8" width="1" height="2"/>
      <rect x="1" y="10" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="4" y="10" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="6" y="10" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="9" y="10" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="12" y="10" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="15" y="10" width="1" height="2"/>
      <rect x="0" y="12" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="3" y="12" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="6" y="12" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="8" y="12" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="11" y="12" width="2" height="2"/><rect x="17" y="12" width="2" height="2"/>
      <rect x="10" y="14" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="13" y="14" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="15" y="14" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="18" y="14" width="1" height="2"/>
      <rect x="8" y="16" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="11" y="16" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="14" y="16" width="2" height="1"/>
      <rect x="9" y="18" width="1" height="2"/><rect x="12" y="18" width="2" height="1"/><rect x="15" y="18" width="1" height="2"/>
      <rect x="8" y="20" width="1" height="1"/><rect x="11" y="20" width="3" height="1"/>
    </g></svg>
  </div>
  <div class="meta">
    <p><strong>Representación impresa</strong> de la Nota De Crédito Electrónica.</p>
    <p>Consulte la validez en <strong>sunat.gob.pe</strong> con el RUC del emisor y el número del comprobante.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:6px;">Firmante: {{ doc.company.ruc }} · Manufacturas Andina Textil S.A.C.</p>
    <p class="hash">Hash: 3f8a21bc9d7e04a6c2f1b8e0d4a7c9f2e5b6d8a1</p>
  </div>
  <div class="stamp">
    <span class="badge">● CPE SUNAT</span>
    <div class="line">Documento electrónico emitido conforme al RCP SUNAT.</div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
